title: Coding is fun!
post_body: I love coding. It feels great being able to build an application completely from scratch! I've learned so much during my Northwestern Bootcamp!

title: The Power of Google
post_body: It's impossible to store everything in your brain. Whenever I get stuck when building an application, I turn to Google to see how others have fixed the problem. Some of my favorite resources are Youtube, StackOverflow, and Medium articles from other coders.
